### Required auth edits (non-breaking)
Update emerald/teal utility classes to token-based classes:
- In [apps/web/src/components/sign-in-form.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/components/sign-in-form.tsx) and [apps/web/src/components/sign-up-form.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/components/sign-up-form.tsx):
  - Replace `focus:border-emerald-500/50 focus:ring-emerald-500/20` with `focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px]`.
  - Replace `bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700` button styling with `bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-primary-foreground` (already provided by `<AuthLoadingButton />` if it composes `Button` styles).
  - Replace link color `text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300` with `text-primary hover:text-primary/90` or `text-brand-secondary` if using secondary accent.
  - Replace background gradient `from-emerald-400 to-teal-600` with `from-[color:var(--color-brand-primary-400)] to-[color:var(--color-brand-secondary-600)]` or semantic gradient utilities using CSS variables.

### Motion & focus patterns
- Use `motion/react` only.
- Preserve focus ring contract: `focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ring/50` as seen in [button.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/components/ui/button.tsx) and [index.css](mdc:apps/web/src/index.css).

### Radius and surfaces
- Interactive: `rounded-md`
- Containers: `rounded-xl`
- Dialogs: `rounded-lg`
Values come from `--radius-*` in [apps/web/src/index.css](mdc:apps/web/src/index.css).

### Sidebar tokens
Use existing sidebar token set from [apps/web/src/index.css](mdc:apps/web/src/index.css). Active item styling should employ `data-[active=true]:bg-sidebar-accent` and `data-[active=true]:font-medium`.

### Accessibility
- Keep AA contrast minimum (OKLCH scales provided are suitable). Avoid `aria-hidden` on focusables, include keyboard parity on all actions.

